  id: ubuntu_apt_update
  displayName: sudo apt update
  rulesText: at the start of each turn, look at the top 2 cards of your draw pile and add the cheaper one to your hand (you choose ties).
  flavorText: there's a package for that.
  designNotes: start-of-turn peek top 2, compare cost, player picks on tie, add chosen to hand; card-selection/advantage passive; must feel impactful within a 3-turn fight; no stacking/scaling.
